It didn't ruin the viewing pleasure. As I said, it's still better than all the other torrents I tried. They were all unwatchable, because their audio had gaps. Your release is the only one so far that is watchable. The reason why I thought it sounds like cam is due to a high level of mid-frequencies which causes the impression of a background noise. And I guess it's already in the source and not because of the bitrate. Because all your other encodings are always top-notch. By the way, I appreaciate your work very much. You do a great job and your encodings are very good at such file size. Thanks a lot! Keep it coming.
